"フェースを使用することを推奨します。<indexterm class=\"singular"
"\"><primary>RabbitMQ</primary></indexterm><indexterm class=\"singular"
"\"><primary>logging/monitoring</primary><secondary>RabbitMQ web management "
"interface</secondary></indexterm> Enable it on your cloud controller:"
