"inherently has access to the database. With regard to performance, "
"<literal>nova-compute</literal> calls to the database are single-threaded "
"and blocking. This creates a performance bottleneck because database "
"requests are fulfilled serially rather than in parallel.<indexterm class="
"\"singular\"><primary>conductors</primary></indexterm><indexterm class="
"\"singular\"><primary>design considerations</primary><secondary>conductor "
"services</secondary></indexterm>"
msgstr ""
